---
// Newsletter signup component with email capture
---

<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-accent-600 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white text-center">
  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Get Weekly AI Tool Updates</h3>
  <p class="text-primary-100 mb-6 max-w-md mx-auto">
    Stay ahead with our curated list of the best AI tools. No spam, just valuable insights.
  </p>

  <form class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 max-w-md mx-auto">
    <input
      type="email"
      placeholder="Enter your email"
      required
      class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg bg-white/10 border border-white/20 text-white placeholder-white/60 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/50"
    />
    <button
      type="submit"
      class="bg-white text-primary-700 hover:bg-gray-100 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors whitespace-nowrap"
    >
      Subscribe Free
    </button>
  </form>

  <p class="text-xs text-primary-200 mt-4">
    Join 5,000+ creators and developers. Unsubscribe anytime.
  </p>
</div>
